CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: At Bolt Projects Holdings, Inc., we are driven by the belief that nature holds the key to solving our greatest challenges. Every day, we draw inspiration from the remarkable materials we engage with, channeling our passion into creating innovative products designed to address the needs of a resource-limited world. As a venture-backed, idea-driven company, we are led by a team of world-class talent and experienced executives from the technology and apparel industries. Our mission is to transform visionary concepts into impactful solutions, pushing the boundaries of whats possible to make a meaningful difference.
